# Component Conventions

- All interactive components use `"use client"` directive
- Functional components only — no class components
- Access state via `useStackshift()` Zustand hook with selectors
- Use Tailwind utility classes exclusively — no CSS modules or styled-components
- Icons from `lucide-react` (import individually)
- Fetch API routes via `fetch("/api/...", { method: "POST", body: JSON.stringify(payload) })`

## Store Access Pattern

```typescript
const { url, setUrl, goTo } = useStackshift();
```

## Naming

- Step components: `{Name}Step.tsx` in `src/components/steps/`
- Panel/overlay components: `{Name}Panel.tsx` in `src/components/`
- One component per file, named export matching filename

## Design Tokens (Tailwind)

- Backgrounds: `bg-paper`, `bg-card`, `bg-ink`
- Text: `text-ink`, `text-muted`, `text-accent`
- Borders: `border-line`, `border-2`
- Shadows: `shadow-hard`, `shadow-hard-sm`, `shadow-btn-accent`
- Fonts: `font-serif` (headings), `font-sans` (body), `font-mono` (code/data)
- Animations: `animate-fade-in`, `animate-stage-in`
